Detailed Description

A Find2Provider is a find provider, which takes a second column and filter rule. The conditions are connected using a logical AND. NOTE: No writing is possible on a FindProvider. Use GetChildRow to get the row of the child provider and update the child provider directly. See also: Provider, FilterProvider, DataItem, FilterRule, FindProvider.
